OL,3,CMan filmed holding swan by its neck in
OL,4,CCaerphilly has charges dropped
OL,6,FCharges against a man who was filmed
OL,7,Fcarrying a swan by its neck near
OL,8,FCaerphilly Castle in December have
OL,9,Fbeen dropped.
OL,11,FThe man in his 30s had been due to
OL,12,Fstand trial for the offence under the
OL,13,FWildlife and Countryside Act 1981 at
OL,14,FNewport Magistrates Court on Tuesday
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FBut the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,18,F(CPS) said the charges had been
OL,19,F"discontinued on legal evidential
OL,20,Fgrounds".
