OL,3,CMan filmed holding swan by its neck in
OL,4,CCaerphilly has charges dropped
OL,6,FBody-worn footage showed the man
OL,7,Fpushing a female police officer inside
OL,8,Fa property in 2023. The man had been
OL,9,Ftold he could not give his partner a
OL,10,Fswig of vodka while she was in the
OL,11,Fprocess of being arrested for a
OL,12,Fseparate offence.
OL,14,FRobert Reid, prosecuting, said there
OL,15,Fhad been a "certain menace in the
OL,16,Fatmosphere" while the man's partner
OL,17,Fwas being handcuffed, and his assault
OL,18,Fon the officer then followed.
