OL,3,CMan filmed holding swan by its neck in
OL,4,CCaerphilly has charges dropped
OL,6,FDarren Bishop, representing the
OL,7,Fdefendant, pointed to the fact the man
OL,8,Fapologised to the officer quickly
OL,9,Fafter the incident and accepted his
OL,10,Farrest for the offence.
OL,12,FMr Bishop said his client has been
OL,13,Fusing his time in custody to enrol on
OL,14,Ftwo courses.
OL,16,FThe judge said it was an "unpleasant
OL,17,Fassault and an unnecessary offence"
OL,18,Fand handed down a number of fines for
OL,19,Fassault of an emergency worker and
OL,20,Ffailure to attend a hearing.
